{"tid":462130,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"[召集內向無社交巴絲] 想每個月定期搞個野餐聚","createTime":"2017-11-08T09:39:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-08T09:56:09.000Z","uid":139272,"like":2,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"58bd658af5712f4f5b4b02e1fe7960ea9833d343","tid":462130,"uid":139272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T09:39:58.000Z","msg":"到秋天，又係野餐既季節!! <br />\n<br />\n有無人平日都比較內向，又唔敢去識新朋友?<br />\n手機平時都無人搵自己，靜到好似無開電話咁<br />\n去親社交場合都係比人忽視，好難同人拉近距離<br />\n多數時間都起屋企，完全無意慾去接觸外界<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n黎緊就計劃緊搞一個每月定期既野餐聚，<br />\n期望大家都一齊去認識新朋友仔，又可以享受一班人野餐既樂趣! <br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">由於都係想召集同路人(單機為主)，所以活躍巴絲就無份了Sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n野餐既氣氛會比較輕鬆隨和，唔會逼大家social架(可以放心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n人數方面都唔會預好多，預計6-8個人<br />\n人少少自然傾都可以多點空間嘛<br />\n<br />\n第一次野餐聚既地點，初步決定起啟德郵輪碼頭公園搞! <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://wow.esdlife.com/attachment/201611/18/30967_1479482521yuP5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwow.esdlife.com%2Fattachment%2F201611%2F18%2F30967_1479482521yuP5.jpg&h=659a4de3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n時間日期暫時未確定，但應該都會係星期六/日下午!!!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果有興趣既巴絲可以起下面留名(CD-rom也歡迎)<br />\n同埋都起TG到contact我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等我預計下可唔可以成行! <br />\n<br />\nTG: @RM_CyberY"},{"pid":"a3729114cc2d8e50e27ffa1da7c3207be2f022aa","tid":462130,"uid":140,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T09:43:32.000Z","msg":"真內向既話一定唔會出"},{"pid":"d4833c7b8b115ed6a2d4df0fe10dc5d5b7f43b3e","tid":462130,"uid":34676,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T09:44:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真內向既話一定唔會出</blockquote><br />\nagger<br />\n出嚟一定個個偽毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不了"},{"pid":"ffc49c08b247221164ad8b7f961312eb5e22e1fd","tid":462130,"uid":139272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T09:44:30.000Z","msg":"咁快就有巴打聯絡左我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71eeefd9aa40b566a2fb69be0f9e2cdcff72b4af","tid":462130,"uid":139272,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T09:45:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真內向既話一定唔會出</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你咁講都係，但內向既人其實都想識下朋友架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"292ee535cca355ba77495febc73deaef11121811","tid":462130,"uid":53223,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T09:47:30.000Z","msg":"金鐘金拱門見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc814a6fe5b64c45019390b52dcacea877e7186d","tid":462130,"uid":139272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T09:48:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>真內向既話一定唔會出</blockquote><br />\nagger<br />\n出嚟一定個個偽毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不了</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又唔一定既，加上我都唔希望有偽毒出現<br />\n咁就搞到成個聚會無哂意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e340a945f50c4da66b677f49bd6e1580830a587","tid":462130,"uid":139272,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T09:49:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>金鐘金拱門見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啟德啊巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"662292c579fbefeae91f203d09b1dfda97b69150","tid":462130,"uid":126293,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T09:52:44.000Z","msg":"出到黎得攪手出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n十年前golden都有個獨人組,出黎靜到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8365de8f086c0c3f6531fb4323411207ec1820a","tid":462130,"uid":139272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"re