blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打有無邊度好推介?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5466abb5d2881269f1fa7e0c594860ce9657e581","tid":462130,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T08:20:52.000Z","msg":"諗起都尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0b6b61fa336c984a9e3c9c65cbe8718fc97f709","tid":462130,"uid":125210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T10:20:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我一星期去一次野餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n差唔多去哂全港草地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打有無邊度好推介?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n靜啲可以去中山紀念公園，星期六日都唔算多人又有海景睇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/09/180759_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F09%2F180759_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=efdfac1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/09/181230_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F09%2F181230_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f0c2a561&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/09/181239_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F09%2F181239_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=35ada9cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n想熱鬧啲多啲野玩可以去西九，差唔多個個星期都有活動。今個星期日我都會去西九野餐同參加工作坊。不過堅係多賓賓，要早啲去霸位。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佐敦谷就不了，好多蚊。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},